Name: Don't Notice Me
About the game: Don't Notice Me is a narrative adventure game where you navigate high school politics, deceive authority figures, pick locks, break into rooms and solve murder mysteries: Typical teenage activities! Mika Kittinger has worked up the courage to give Elliot Chase a love letter. However, she immediately regrets her decision and sets out to get that letter back. Help her on her adventure of hunting down his address, breaking into his house and finding the letter before getting caught. Snooping through Elliot's room is a key element of solving puzzles. What weird things is he hiding in his room and is any of it clues to his passwords? Where will you find Elliot's address? How do you get into his house? What's with the mysterious briefcase? There seems to be something going on under the surface, but what's most important is finding the letter. When you live dangerously, you need to be prepared for any kind of outcome whether its good, bad or somewhere in between. You may even breathe heavily through your nose.
